data.description: Welcome to your dream townhouse in the desirable Auberry Place gated community, where luxury meets comfort! This stunning two-story residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a two-car garage, and a wealth of upgrades that redefine modern living.  As you step inside, you are greeted by a spacious living room and dining area, adorned with crown molding and featuring 9-foot ceilings that create an atmosphere of elegance and openness. All upgrades were done 3 years ago. The recently renovated kitchen is a chef's delight, showcasing newer stainless steel appliances, pristine quartz countertops, and a stylish new sink. The heart of this home is not only functional but also a visual feast.  Entertaining is a joy with the glass sliding door leading to the backyard oasis. This corner unit boasts a generous backyard with lush turf, carefully designed hardscape, and a flourishing lemon tree laden with citrus treasures. Picture yourself enjoying al fresco meals or simply basking in the California sunshine in this private retreat.  The list of upgrades goes on, with fresh French grey paint adorning the entire residence, new plush carpeting underfoot, and brand-new interior doors adding a touch of sophistication. The thoughtful inclusion of plantation shutters provides both privacy and style, while the newly installed fan in the master bedroom ensures comfort year-round.  This townhouse is not just a home; it's a masterpiece. From the built-in entertainment center for your TV to the timeless travertine floors, every detail has been carefully curated to enhance your living experience. New outlets, switches, and USB outlets further exemplify the commitment to modern convenience.  Additional features include a newer Rheem water heater for efficiency and peace of mind. With access to the community pool within the secure Auberry Place gated community, you can enjoy resort-style amenities just steps from your front door.  Seize the opportunity to make this townhouse your own – a place where luxury, comfort, and style converge in perfect harmony. Schedule a viewing today and experience the lifestyle awaiting you at Auberry Place. Your dream home is now a reality!
